{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"35270065-534b-4f2a-8bce-d2a78036f077","content":"No workflow files found in this directory. Since there's no repo to inspect, here's a concise guide for switching to NuGet trusted publishing (OIDC):\n\n### What to change\n\n**1. NuGet.org setup** — Register your GitHub repo as a trusted publisher at:\n`nuget.org → Your Package → Manage → Trusted Publishers → Add GitHub Repository`\n\nSet the allowed workflow file, branch, and environment.\n\n**2. Workflow changes:**\n\n```yaml\njobs:\n  publish:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    environment: nuget          # must match what you configured on nuget.org\n    permissions:\n      id-token: write           # required for OIDC token\n      contents: read\n\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      - uses: actions/setup-dotnet@v4\n        with:\n          dotnet-version: '8.x'\n\n      # Replace your old push step:\n      #   dotnet nuget push ... --api-key ${{ secrets.NUGET_API_KEY }}\n      # With:\n      - name: Push to NuGet (trusted publishing)\n        run: dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n```\n\n**Key differences from API-key publishing:**\n\n| Before (API key) | After (OIDC) |\n|---|---|\n| `secrets.NUGET_API_KEY` | No secret needed |\n| No `permissions` block | `id-token: write` required |\n| No `environment` | `environment:` must match NuGet config |\n| `--api-key ${{ secrets.NUGET_API_KEY }}` | No `--api-key` flag |\n\n**3. Delete** the `NUGET_API_KEY` repository secret once verified.\n\n> **Note:** `dotnet nuget push` automatically detects the OIDC token from the `ACTIONS_ID_TOKEN_REQUEST_URL` / `ACTIONS_ID_TOKEN_REQUEST_TOKEN` env vars that GitHub injects when `id-token: write` is set. Requires .NET SDK 8.0.400+ or the `dotnet-nuget-push` action.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"0fb4421c-76cf-4048-8f81-2d8e0883553d","outputTokens":525,"requestId":"B454:15666D:7251EBC:7DCED78:69F1572B"},"id":"31282eac-33e5-4013-9248-a2edd572d77b","timestamp":"2026-04-29T00:56:24.141Z","parentId":"7af5be6c-472d-4f2b-b6cf-74cd2aafdbe5"}
